info.title: Greenway Health Prime Suite API
info.description: Test the Greenway Health Prime Suite API services using I/O Docs.  Please note this is a set of examples and not our full listing of Prime Suite API.  You can view our written documentation. Page contains a set of Prime Suite API examples - Please reference the Prime Suite API Doc Page for full list of available Prime Suite API.

externalDocs.description: You can also view our written documentation.
